Definition: time period following childbirth when the mother's uterus shrinks and the other functional and anatomic changes of pregnancy are resolved
Example: a perinatologist cared for her during the puerperium
Synonyms: adj, pert, puerperal, time_period, time, period, following, childbirth, when, the, mother, s, uterus, shrinks, and, other, functional, anatomic, changes, of, pregnancy, are, resolved, a, perinatologist, cared, for, her, during
Category: noun.time
